document.full_text: cam fowler scored the game-winning goal in overtime, after teemu selanne had forced the extra period with sevens seconds remaining, to help the anaheim ducks beat the dallas stars 4-3 wednesday.
document.title: anaheim ducks leave it late to bring dallas stars down to earth
